⚠️ Important Notes
MinIO Password: The MinIO password is set to YOUR_MINIO_PASSWORD in the .env file. You should change this to a secure password.
Security: These are default development credentials. For production use, you should:
Change all default passwords
Use strong, unique passwords
Consider using environment variables for sensitive data
First Login: Use the admin credentials (admin/123) to access the Casdoor admin panel and LobeChat application initially.
The setup script (setup.sh) can generate random passwords for better security, but the current configuration uses these default values.
